org.apache.flex.compiler.internal.definitions

Class MetadataDefinitionBase

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.apache.flex.compiler.internal.definitions.DefinitionBase
      • org.apache.flex.compiler.internal.definitions.MetadataDefinitionBase
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    IDefinition, IDocumentableDefinition, IMetadataDefinition, IDefinitionSet
    Direct Known Subclasses:
    EffectDefinition, EventDefinition, StyleDefinition

    public abstract class MetadataDefinitionBase
extends DefinitionBase
implements IMetadataDefinition
    This is the abstract base class for definitions in the symbol table that that are declared by metadata tags on other definitions.
